---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | WEUX Content Finder" description="Privacy policy for WEUX Content Finder: information on data processing, hosting, external links, and your rights under GDPR.">
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="wrap nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo" aria-label="WEUX Content Finder home">
        <img class="nav-logo-mark" src="/header-logo-mark.svg" alt="" />
        <img class="nav-logo-wordmark" src="/header-logo-wordmark.svg" alt="WEUX Content Finder" />
      </a>
      <div class="nav-menu">
        <a href="/#problem" class="nav-link">Problem</a>
        <a href="/#coverage" class="nav-link">Coverage</a>
        <a href="/#pro" class="nav-link">Pro</a>
        <a href="/#comparison" class="nav-link">Free vs Pro</a>
        <a href="/#usecases" class="nav-link">Use Cases</a>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-cta">
        <a href="/#comparison" class="btn btn-outline">Compare</a>
        <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/weux-content-finder/" class="btn btn-dark" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get Free</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="legal-page">
    <section class="legal-hero">
      <div class="wrap legal-hero-inner">
        <a href="/" class="legal-back">Back to home</a>
        <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="h-section">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="body-l">How WEUX Content Finder handles website data, hosting, links, and GDPR rights.</p>
        <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: June 2026</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="legal-body">
      <div class="wrap legal-grid">
        <aside class="legal-side">
          <p>This website does not use tracking or marketing cookies. Fonts are served locally with the website assets.</p>
        </aside>
        <div class="legal-content">
          <section>
            <h2>1. Data Protection at a Glance</h2>
            <p>We treat your personal data confidentially and in accordance with the statutory data protection regulations, including the GDPR, and this privacy policy.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>2. Responsible Body</h2>
            <p>
              Marc Weidemüller<br />
              WEUX Studio<br />
              Elisabeth-Flügge-Straße 6b<br />
              22337 Hamburg<br />
              Germany<br />
              Email: <a href="#" class="protected-contact" data-contact-kind="email" data-contact-value="aGVsbG9Ad2V1eC5zdHVkaW8=">Reveal email</a>
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>3. Hosting</h2>
            <p>This website is hosted on Cloudflare Pages (Cloudflare Inc., 101 Townsend St., San Francisco, CA 94107, USA). Cloudflare acts as a processor on our behalf. A data processing agreement is in place. Data transfers to the USA are based on the EU-US Data Privacy Framework.</p>
            <p>When you visit this website, your IP address, browser information, and the pages you view are processed by Cloudflare for the purpose of delivering and securing the website content.</p>
            <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR, based on our legitimate interest in operating and securing this website.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>4. Cookies</h2>
            <p>This website does not use tracking or marketing cookies. No cookie consent banner is required.</p>
            <p><strong>Legal basis:</strong> Section 25(2) No. 2 TDDDG for technically necessary functions only.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>5. External Links</h2>
            <p>This website contains links to external services, including WordPress.org, Lemon Squeezy, and WEUX Studio. Clicking these links may result in data being transmitted to the respective service. Please refer to their privacy policies for details on their data processing.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p>Under the GDPR, you have the following rights:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Right to access your personal data under Art. 15 GDPR</li>
              <li>Right to rectification under Art. 16 GDPR</li>
              <li>Right to erasure under Art. 17 GDPR</li>
              <li>Right to restriction of processing under Art. 18 GDPR</li>
              <li>Right to data portability under Art. 20 GDPR</li>
              <li>Right to object under Art. 21 GDPR</li>
            </ul>
            <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="#" class="protected-contact" data-contact-kind="email" data-contact-value="aGVsbG9Ad2V1eC5zdHVkaW8=">Reveal email</a>.</p>
            <p>You also have the right to lodge a complaint with the competent supervisory authority:</p>
            <p>
              Der Hamburgische Beauftragte für Datenschutz und Informationsfreiheit<br />
              Ludwig-Erhard-Straße 22, 20459 Hamburg<br />
              <a href="https://datenschutz-hamburg.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://datenschutz-hamburg.de</a>
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <div class="cta-footer legal-footer">
    <footer>
      <div class="footer-shell">
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="footer-inner">
            <div class="footer-brand">
              <a href="/" class="footer-logo" aria-label="WEUX Content Finder home">
                <img src="/footer-logo.svg" alt="WEUX Content Finder" />
              </a>
              <p>The WordPress content search tool for production sites. Find where content is managed and open the right editor.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-cols">
              <div><h4>Product</h4><ul><li><a href="/#coverage">Search Coverage</a></li><li><a href="/#pro">Pro Features</a></li><li><a href="/#comparison">Free vs Pro</a></li><li><a href="/#usecases">Use Cases</a></li></ul></div>
              <div><h4>Resources</h4><ul><li><a href="/#trust">Trust & Safety</a></li><li><a href="/#faq">FAQs</a></li><li><a href="/#problem">The Problem</a></li><li><a href="/#workflow">How It Works</a></li></ul></div>
              <div><h4>Get Started</h4><ul><li><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/weux-content-finder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Download Free</a></li><li><a href="/#download">Upgrade to Pro</a></li><li><a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/weux-content-finder/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WordPress.org</a></li></ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="footer-bottom">
            <span class="footer-copyright">© 2026 WEUX Content Finder. Built for WordPress editing screens, not database migrations. <span class="footer-legal-links"><a href="/imprint/">Imprint</a><a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a></span></span>
            <span class="footer-credit-text">Crafted for WordPress teams by <a href="https://weux.studio/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="footer-credit"><svg width="64" height="46" viewBox="0 0 64 46" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M29.2872 11.4831L23.832 1.70528L15.7996 1.70526L25.1425 18.4519L29.2872 11.4831Z" fill="#F3D054"/><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M28.8769 10.6603L34.332 0.882529L42.3645 0.882502L33.0215 17.6291L28.8769 10.6603Z" fill="#F3D054"/><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M29.0598 24.7318L21.8841 37.5938L0.100727 0.967424L0.211486 0.882745L8.23723 0.882885L21.7021 23.5224L24.9152 17.7632L28.8314 10.5827L36.5273 23.5224L49.1583 0.882787L57.1907 0.88276L36.7093 37.5938L29.0598 24.7318Z" fill="#E8E7E7"/></svg>weux.studio</a></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
